summary: This is an email from an FBI agent to an AIMS recipient regarding a Delaware corporation named L.S.J, LLC, which uses a US Virgin Islands address. The email includes an attachment and references a subpoena rider, indicating investigative interest in the entity's financial structure.

events.title: Email regarding L.S.J, LLC subpoena rider
events.description: An FBI Senior Financial Investigator sends an email concerning a Delaware corporation, L.S.J, LLC, and attaches a subpoena rider document.

locations: 6100 Red Hook Quarter, Suite 8-3, St Thomas, USVI 00802
keyFacts: The document is an email dated August 7, 2019, from an FBI Senior Financial Investigator.
The subject of the email is a Delaware corporation named L.S.J, LLC.
L.S.J, LLC uses a business address in St. Thomas, U.S. Virgin Islands.
The email references and attaches a subpoena rider, indicating an active financial investigation.
The correspondence is part of the Epstein-related financial investigation data set.
